agents.name: Baseline Solver for Agentified OpenCaptchaWorld Benchmark

agentbeats_dev_details.architecture: Spider 2.0 framework with code agent that interacts with A2A protocol. The evaluator is a green agent that loads Spider2-Snow tasks, sends them to target agents, executes SQL on Snowflake, and compares results.
agentbeats_dev_details.purpose: Evaluating Language Models on Real-World Enterprise Text-to-SQL Workflows with complex cloud or local data across various database systems
agentbeats_dev_details.goal: Evaluate agent capabilities in solving real-world enterprise text-to-SQL workflow problems with databases containing over 1,000 columns, requiring understanding of database metadata, dialect documentation, and codebases
agentbeats_dev_details.approach: A2A (Agent-to-Agent) protocol-based evaluation where the green agent loads tasks from Spider2-Snow dataset, sends tasks to target agent, expects SQL queries in DataPart JSON format, executes on Snowflake, and returns machine-readable metrics
